 via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aReminiscingvFiction. 0aReminiscingxFiction. 0aSuicidal behaviorvFiction. 0aSuicidal behaviorxFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aVincent, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVincent, Paul.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021646240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300216462423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300216462/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles